description: Returns metadata that's related to the images in a repository in a public registry.

parameters.name: repositoryName
parameters.description: The repository that contains the images to describe.

parameters.name: imageIds
parameters.description: The list of image IDs for the requested repository. (dict) --- An object with identifying information for an Amazon ECR image. imageDigest (string) --- The sha256 digest of the image manifest. imageTag (string) --- The tag that's used for the image.

nested_params.name: imageDigest
nested_params.description: The sha256 digest of the image manifest.

nested_params.name: imageTag
nested_params.description: The tag that's used for the image.

nested_items.name: imageDetails
nested_items.description: A list of  ImageDetail objects that contain data about the image.

nested_items.name: registryId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services account ID that's associated with the public registry where this image belongs.

nested_items.name: repositoryName
nested_items.description: The name of the repository where this image belongs.

nested_items.name: imageDigest
nested_items.description: The sha256 digest of the image manifest.

nested_items.name: imageTags
nested_items.description: The list of tags that's associated with this image.

nested_items.name: imageSizeInBytes
nested_items.description: The size, in bytes, of the image in the repository.

nested_items.name: imagePushedAt
nested_items.description: The date and time, expressed in standard JavaScript date format, that the current image was pushed to the repository at.

nested_items.name: imageManifestMediaType
nested_items.description: The media type of the image manifest.

nested_items.name: artifactMediaType
nested_items.description: The artifact media type of the image.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The nextToken value to include in a future DescribeImages request. When the results of a DescribeImages request exceed maxResults, you can use this value to retrieve the next page of results. If there are no more results to return, this value is null.
